<subSubSection pageId="23" pageNumber="130" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="23.[1468,2678,705,1487]" pageId="23" pageNumber="130">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1470,1817,1336,1369]" pageId="23" pageNumber="130">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Research is needed to understand biology, ecology, and conservation status of the Ethiopian Hare.
</paragraph>
